      <title>瑞士支持欧盟对六名哈马斯支持者实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/switzerland-backs-eu-sanctions-against-six-hamas-supporters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士政府周三在一份声明中表示，瑞士正在对六名参与资助哈马斯和巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战组织的个人实施金融制裁和旅行限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/switzerland-backs-eu-sanctions-against-six-hamas-supporters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:06:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>曾经被嘲笑的议长候选人汤姆·埃默（Tom Emmer）饰演迈克·约翰逊（Mike Johnson）摇摇欲坠，向特朗普示好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/trump-courted-by-once-scorned-speaker-hopeful-tom-emmer-as-mike-johnson-teeters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五个月前，唐纳德·特朗普在社交媒体上发了一条严厉的帖子，让汤姆·埃默成为众议院议长的希望破灭，这位前总统在海湖庄园的一场筹款活动上赞扬了他，为这位明尼苏达州国会议员赢得了超过 30 万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/trump-courted-by-once-scorned-speaker-hopeful-tom-emmer-as-mike-johnson-teeters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西拒绝美国放弃乙醇进口关税的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/brazil-rebuffs-us-pressure-to-abandon-tariffs-on-ethanol-imports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[农业部长卡洛斯·法瓦罗表示，尽管拜登政府提出“严厉”抱怨，巴西仍将维持对美国乙醇进口的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/brazil-rebuffs-us-pressure-to-abandon-tariffs-on-ethanol-imports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 14:54:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国将四分之一的对外援助预算用于国内难民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/uk-spends-quarter-of-foreign-aid-budget-domestically-on-refugees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[政府监管机构表示，英国超过四分之一的国际援助预算用于国内寻求庇护者和难民，这给向海外寻求支持的资金带来了进一步的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/uk-spends-quarter-of-foreign-aid-budget-domestically-on-refugees</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 14:37:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士宣布六月中旬举行乌克兰和平峰会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/switzerland-announces-summit-on-ukraine-peace-plan-on-june-15-16</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士将于6月15日至16日主办一次高级别会议，以巩固全球对乌克兰倡导的和平框架的支持，该框架将结束与俄罗斯的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/switzerland-announces-summit-on-ukraine-peace-plan-on-june-15-16</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 13:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯工厂争先恐后地从当地供应商那里购买无人机防御系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/russian-factories-rush-to-buy-drone-defense-from-local-suppliers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰无人机袭击的加剧迫使俄罗斯公司寻找方法来保护自己的工厂和工厂，而不是依赖军队，这为雷达和战争装备生产商提供了意想不到的推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/russian-factories-rush-to-buy-drone-defense-from-local-suppliers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 13:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国赤字超出预期，给马克龙带来压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/french-deficit-to-widen-even-more-raising-pressure-on-macron</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国政府表示，随着埃马纽埃尔·马克龙削减开支的压力加大，其赤字将比预期更大——或者寻找新的国家收入来源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/french-deficit-to-widen-even-more-raising-pressure-on-macron</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 12:54:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克废除分拆计划，东欧最大公用事业公司获得救济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/east-eu-s-top-utility-gets-some-relief-as-czechs-drop-split-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克立法者放弃了一项旨在帮助政府改造占主导地位的电力公司CEZ AS的提案，结束了与投资者长达一年的争执，投资者对股价造成压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/east-eu-s-top-utility-gets-some-relief-as-czechs-drop-split-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 10:41:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统将在议会投票中惨败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/south-korea-opposition-keeps-parliament-majority-forecast-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈的保守派联盟在新议会投票中将遭遇重大挫折，这将使他在余下三年的任期内处于弱势，并可能阻碍他的投资者友好政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/south-korea-opposition-keeps-parliament-majority-forecast-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:03:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大亨弗里德曼和艾文在与欧盟制裁的法庭诉讼中获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/tycoon-fridman-wins-eu-sanctions-appeal-over-alleged-putin-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯大亨米哈伊尔·弗里德曼（Mikhail Fridman）和他的商业伙伴彼得·阿文（Petr Aven）在对抗欧盟因涉嫌支持弗拉基米尔·普京总统及其对乌克兰的战争而实施的制裁的斗争中取得了意外的胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/tycoon-fridman-wins-eu-sanctions-appeal-over-alleged-putin-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:11:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
